General.Name: BTS Group AB Series B
General.Description: BTS Group AB (publ) operates as a professional services firm. The company operates through BTS North America, BTS Europe, BTS Other Markets, and APG segments. It also provides strategy execution and business transformation, leadership readiness and development, talent acquisition and succession, and go to market services. BTS Group AB (publ) was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
